                            <comment id="12979048" author="fmeschbe" created="Sat, 8 Jan 2011 01:00:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in Rev. 1056579&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add configuration properties to set whether NIO is to be used for HTTP(S):&lt;br/&gt;
   org.apache.felix.http.nio - (boolean) whether to use NIO for HTTP or not, default is true&lt;br/&gt;
   org.apache.felix.https.nio - (boolean) whether to use NIO for HTTPS or not, default is to use&lt;br/&gt;
         the value of the org.apache.felix.http.nio property&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Does that suite your need ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
